            googletag.pubads().addEventListener('slotRequested', function(event) {
               var adCode = event.slot.getSlotElementId();
               //HACK
               if ( adCode === 'gpt_unit_/31961696/RYM_Interstitial_AdX_0' ) {
                  adCode = 'div-gpt-ad-1465817209349-125';
               }
               if ( adCode === 'gpt_unit_/31961696/RYM_BottomAnchor_AdX_0' ) {
                  adCode = 'div-gpt-ad-1465817209349-229';
               }

               if ( rymads[adCode] ) {
                  console.log(`*** rym.ads: GAM fetched (${adCode} - ${rymads[adCode].description})`);
               } else {
                  console.log(`*** rym.ads: GAM fetched non-tracked code ${adCode}`);
               }
            });

            googletag.pubads().addEventListener('slotOnload', function(event) {
               //HACK
               var adCode = event.slot.getSlotElementId();
               if ( adCode === 'gpt_unit_/31961696/RYM_Interstitial_AdX_0' ) {
                  adCode = 'div-gpt-ad-1465817209349-125';
               }
               if ( adCode === 'gpt_unit_/31961696/RYM_BottomAnchor_AdX_0' ) {
                  adCode = 'div-gpt-ad-1465817209349-229';
               }

               _doPostRender(adCode);
               if ( rymads[adCode] ) {
                  console.log(`*** rym.ads: GAM rendered (${adCode} - ${rymads[adCode].description})`);
               } else {
                  console.log(`*** rym.ads: GAM rendered non-tracked code ${adCode}`);
               }
             });

            googletag.pubads().setTargeting('site', ['rateyourmusic']);
            googletag.pubads().setTargeting('pagetype', ['chart']);
            googletag.pubads().setTargeting('logged_in', 'false');

            googletag.pubads().setTargeting('enable_floating', ['true']);
            googletag.pubads().setTargeting('enable_adhesions', ['true']);

      
            googletag.enableServices();

         });

         (function() {

            var profileVersionId = '';

            if ( purl.indexOf('pwtv=')>0 ) {
               var regexp = /pwtv=(.*?)(&|$)/g;
               var matches = regexp.exec(purl);
               if ( matches.length >= 2 && matches[1].length > 0 ) {

         (function() {
            var purl = window.location.href;
            var url = '//ads.pubmatic.com/AdServer/js/pwt/162157/7704';
            var profileVersionId = '';

            if ( purl.indexOf('pwtv=')>0 ) {
               var regexp = /pwtv=(.*?)(&|$)/g;

               if ( matches.length >= 2 && matches[1].length > 0 ) {
                  profileVersionId = '/'+matches[1];

      <div class="ui_section_overlay"></div>

      <p>There are unlimited ways to filter charts: You can make a personalized chart based on any combination of genres, descriptors, countries, languages and more.</p>

      <div class="page_charts_settings_summary">
         

         <form name="page_chart_query" onSubmit="return false;"  id="page_chart_query" class="page_chart_query chart_type_top object_release date_type_year_decade scope_music

               function destroyAdhesion(slotName) {

            var profileVersionId = '';

            var profileVersionId = '';

               function destroyAdhesion(slotName) {
                  console.log(`rym.ads: calling destroySlot on div-gpt-ad-${slotName}`)

         (function() {
            var purl = window.location.href;
            var url = '//ads.pubmatic.com/AdServer/js/pwt/162157/7704';
            var profileVersionId = '';

            if ( purl.indexOf('pwtv=')>0 ) {

                                          <p>To choose a single year, click the year (e.g. "15" for 2015)</p>
                                          <p>To choose a decade, click the decade (left column)</p>

                                       </div>

                                 <label class="page_chart_query_radio_label" for="page_chart_query_advanced_soundtrack_inclusion_mode_deweight">
                                    <input id="page_chart_query_advanced_soundtrack_inclusion_mode_deweight" name="page_chart_query_advanced_soundtrack_inclusion_mode"  onClick="RYMchart.setInclusionMode('soundtrack', 'deweight');" type="radio"> Include deweighted
                                 </label>

                                 <label class="page_chart_query_radio_label" for="page_chart_query_advanced_soundtrack_inclusion_mode_include">
                                    <input id="page_chart_query_advanced_soundtrack_inclusion_mode_include" name="page_chart_query_advanced_soundtrack_inclusion_mode"  onClick="RYMchart.setInclusionMode('soundtrack', 'include');" type="radio"> Include
                                 </label>

                                 <label class="page_chart_query_radio_label" for="page_chart_query_advanced_soundtrack_inclusion_mode_only">

                                 </label>

                        </div>

                     </div>
                     <div class="clearfix"></div>


         

                     <div class="page_chart_query_create_advanced">

                        <div class="page_chart_query_advanced_show_links_label">
                           <span class="page_chart_query_advanced_show_label page_chart_query_advanced_show_label_show_initial"><a onClick="RYMchart.onClickShowAdvancedOptions();">Show advanced options</a></span>
